interpretation: The "person getting massage" card represents the need for relaxation and self-care. It suggests taking a break from the stresses of daily life and allowing oneself to receive nurturing and healing. This card encourages us to let go of tension and stress and to allow ourselves to be pampered. It can also represent seeking help and support from others, whether it be through physical touch or emotional support. Associated keywords include: self-care, relaxation, pampering, rejuvenation, healing, support, letting go, surrender.
